mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7625db8f46221546674e2496b0544a65b60d203","tid":2233802,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】果然是埃及文明！利物浦球星沙拿出於一片好心，早前拯救了一名晏菲路球場外的無家者。<br />\n利物浦主場以3:1擊敗阿仙奴後，今年28歲的沙拿（Mohamed Salah）在晏菲路附近，出手阻止一班流氓騷擾一名街頭露宿的無家者。<br />\n<br />\n據知，當時沙拿駕駛賓利到油站，發現一名無家者正被一班人圍住騷擾，於是埃及人決定仗義相助，上前趕走了那班好事之徒，事後更到櫃員機提取100鎊給予無家者。<br />\n<br />\n該名無家者已露宿6年，名叫基治，日前接受《太陽報》訪問時讚揚沙拿是「真英雄」，並謂：「他在球場外的行為就像場內為紅軍奮戰一樣厲害，並警告他們『幾年之後你們都可能像他一樣無家可歸』，他是完美的傳奇，過程被附近的閉路電視全程拍下。」<br />\n<br />\n這個世界，就是偽君子太多，真英雄太少，希望沙拿的義行能夠感動更多人"},{"pid":"197ef62e906f04d29197b8eb2c1e226eb263176a","tid":2233802,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031d20c58571073341536cba6c4ad1ff2a9cb91d","tid":2233802,"uid":42246,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"文尼洗廁所 vs 沙拉救流浪漢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同中共做得太多衰野 要不停做d門面野洗底一樣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"咪柒啦，中共有撚洗底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d577a4e2ae1254fb6cde5cb6c1ee2a2c23f08c","tid":2233802,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"197ef62e906f04d29197b8eb2c1e226eb263176a","tid":2233802,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"031d20c58571073341536cba6c4ad1ff2